==製作==
===拍攝===
2012年7月，《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》正式於[[納米比亞|納米比亞]]開拍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/tom-hardy-mad-max-fury-road-start-date-benm-173570/ |title=Tom Hardy Uncertain About 'Mad Max: Fury Road' Start Date [UPDATED] |publisher=Screenrant.com |date=2013-07-23 |accessdate=2013-11-21 |archive-date=2014-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122065923/http://screenrant.com/tom-hardy-mad-max-fury-road-start-date-benm-173570/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他取景地包括{{link-en|波茲山 (新南威爾斯州)|Potts Hill, New South Wales|波茲山}}和{{link-en|凱恩巴克 (新南威爾斯州)|Cranebrook, New South Wales|湖泊彭里斯}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Mad Max: Fury Road to Roar Through Sydney Streets|url=http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=21051&s=News_files|website=Urban Cinefile|accessdate=2015-05-06|date=2015-05-07|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518082810/http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=21051&s=News_files|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年10月，《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》報導，華納兄弟派出高管來監督以維持製作順利<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-sends-studio-representative-380010 |title=Warner Bros. Sends 'Studio Representative' to Namibia to Keep 'Fury Road' on Track (Exclusive) |publisher=Hollywoodreporter.com |date=2012-10-18 |accessdate=2013-11-21 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113225335/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-sends-studio-representative-380010 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年12月17日左右殺青<ref>{{cite web|url=http://twitchfilm.com/2012/12/its-a-wrap-mad-max-fury-road-completes-principal-photography.html|title=It's A Wrap! MAD MAX: FURY ROAD Completes Principal Photography|last=Brown|first=Todd|work=[[Twitch_Film|Twitch Film]]|date=2012-12-16|accessdate=2014-09-25|archive-date=2014-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819210410/http://twitchfilm.com/2012/12/its-a-wrap-mad-max-fury-road-completes-principal-photography.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年2月，納米比亞海岸保護和管理組指控拍攝工作對[[納米布沙漠|納米布沙漠]]的破壞，其中危及到一些植物和動物物種<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Fragile-desert-damaged-by-Mad-Max-film-crew/tabid/418/articleID/289169/Default.aspx| work=3 News NZ| title=Fragile desert 'damaged' by Mad Max film crew| date=2013-03-06| accessdate=2015-05-07| archive-date=2014-07-28| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728144533/http://www.3news.co.nz/Fragile-desert-damaged-by-Mad-Max-film-crew/tabid/418/articleID/289169/Default.aspx| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/mar/05/mad-max-fury-road-namibia | work= The Guardian | title= Mad Max: Fury Road sparks real-life fury with claims of damage to desert | date= 2013-03-05 | accessdate= 2015-05-07 | archive-date= 2013-03-09 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130309001613/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2013/mar/05/mad-max-fury-road-namibia | dead-url= no }}</ref>。然而，納米比亞電影委員會認為，這都是媒體加油添醋的「不當言辭」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thelocationguide.com/blog/2013/03/ng-film-namibia-film-commission-disputes-mad-max-4-location-filming-damage-claim/|title=Namibia Film Commission disputes Mad Max 4 location filming damage claim|last=Goundry|first=Nick|work=The Location Guide|date=2013-03-07|accessdate=2014-09-25|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140925045307/http://www.thelocationguide.com/blog/2013/03/ng-film-namibia-film-commission-disputes-mad-max-4-location-filming-damage-claim/|archive-date=2014-09-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2013年9月，宣布電影將在2013年11月進行補拍<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=108457 |title=Mad Max: Fury Road Going Back for Reshoots |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=2013-09-03 |accessdate=2013-11-21 |archive-date=2013-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906051640/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=108457 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

攝影師[[約翰·西爾|約翰·西爾]]拍完本片就打算退休<ref name="Collider">{{cite web|last1=Radish|first1=Christina|title=MAD MAX: FURY ROAD: 18 Things to Know about the Making of George Miller’s Epic|url=http://collider.com/mad-max-fury-road-18-things-to-know/|website=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|publisher=[[Complex_(magazine)|Complex]]|accessdate=2015-05-01|date=2015-05-01|archive-date=2015-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150523044737/http://collider.com/mad-max-fury-road-18-things-to-know/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他使用[[阿萊Alexa|阿萊Alexa]]和[[佳能_EOS_5D|佳能 EOS 5D]]來拍攝動作場面<ref>{{cite web|title=Cinematographer John Seale captures 'Mad Max: Fury Road'|url=http://www.codexdigital.com/news/cinematographer%20john%20seale%20captures%20mad%20max%20-%20fury%20road|website=[[Codex_Digital|Codex Digital]]|accessdate=2015-05-01|archive-date=2015-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150506235708/http://www.codexdigital.com/news/cinematographer%20john%20seale%20captures%20mad%20max%20-%20fury%20road|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年7月，導演喬治·米勒描述電影：「是個非常簡單的[[寓言|寓言]]故事，幾乎都是圍繞在西方的車輪上」<ref name=guardian>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/jul/28/comic-con-2014-mad-max-fury-road-trailer-release-tom-hardy|title=Comic-Con 2014: Mad Max: Fury Road roars into view|author=<!-- Staff -->|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=2014-07-28|accessdate=2014-09-25|archive-date=2014-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140917093459/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2014/jul/28/comic-con-2014-mad-max-fury-road-trailer-release-tom-hardy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。米勒聲稱，電影90％的場面都是真實呈現的<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/all-the-amazing-visuals-from-the-latest-mad-max-fury-road-trailer-and-what-they-might-mean-2015-4?IR=T|title=All the crazy visuals from the latest Mad Max Fury Road trailer|author=Peter Farquhar|publisher=''[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]]'' (Australia)|date=2015-04-01|accessdate=2015-04-04|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518084857/http://www.businessinsider.com/all-the-amazing-visuals-from-the-latest-mad-max-fury-road-trailer-and-what-they-might-mean-2015-4?IR=T|dead-url=no}}</ref>。特技協調員監督蓋·諾里斯掌管超過150個特技表演，其中還包括了[[太陽劇團|太陽劇團]]的演員與曾參加過[[奧林匹克運動會|奥运会]]的運動员<ref>{{cite web|last1=Brevet|first1=Brad|title=Do Practical Effects Even Matter Anymore? To 'Mad Max' & 'Mission: Impossible'... Yes!|url=http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/do-practical-effects-even-matter-anymore-to-mad-max-mission-impossible-yes-they-do/|website=Rope of Silicon|accessdate=2015-05-05|date=2015-05-05|archive-date=2015-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150506215101/http://www.ropeofsilicon.com/do-practical-effects-even-matter-anymore-to-mad-max-mission-impossible-yes-they-do/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，米勒還邀請了[[伊芙·恩斯勒|伊芙·恩斯勒]]作為顧問，為了女權主義的主題和令人印象深刻的劇本，恩斯勒花了一個星期在納米比亞採訪了當地人有關婦女的暴力問題<ref>{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3850323/mad-max-fury-road-eve-ensler-feminist/|title=Vagina Monologues Writer Eve Ensler: How Mad Max: Fury Road Became a 'Feminist Action Film'|last=Dockterman|first=Eliana|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|date=2015-05-07|accessdate=2015-05-18|archive-date=2015-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150517182110/http://time.com/3850323/mad-max-fury-road-eve-ensler-feminist/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

