==續集==
米勒和麥卡錫在編寫《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》時，他們認為這還有足夠的發展空間，因此又完成了兩份劇本。其中一項劇本為《Mad Max: Furiosa》，米勒期望能在《憤怒道》上映之後接著開拍<ref>Turner, Brook (25 Nov 2011). [http://www.afr.com/p/george_miller_new_script_q1wYu1EFjLM0cyZa4s97fI George Miller’s new script] {{Wayback|url=http://www.afr.com/p/george_miller_new_script_q1wYu1EFjLM0cyZa4s97fI |date=20140407192950 }}. [[The_Australian_Financial_Review|AFR]]. Retrieved 03 Feb 2012.</ref>。2015年3月，湯姆·哈迪在接受《[[君子雜誌|君子雜誌]]》的採訪時透露，他已簽下後續《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》等三部續集片約，但是否會推出續集暫未知<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esquire.co.uk/culture/film-tv/8074/tom-hardy-esquire-interview/|title=Tom Hardy Is Esquire's May Cover Star|author=Miranda Collinge|publisher=''[[Esquire_(magazine)|Esquire]]''|date=2015-03-30|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-date=2015-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150331190806/http://www.esquire.co.uk/culture/film-tv/8074/tom-hardy-esquire-interview/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2015年5月，米勒向《[[連線|連線]]》雜誌透露，「如果（瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道）能成功，那我還有另外兩個故事能講」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wired.com/2015/05/mad-max-fury-road/|title=MAD MAX: WHAT IT TAKES TO MAKE THE MOST INTENSE MOVIE EVER|author=Logan Hill|work=''[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]''|publisher=([[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]])|date=2015-05-11|accessdate=2015-05-12|archive-date=2015-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150514004411/http://www.wired.com/2015/05/mad-max-fury-road|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月，米勒改變了計劃，決定將續集名稱改定為《Mad Max: The Wasteland》<ref>{{cite web|last1=Lussier|first1=Germain|title=George Miller Gives ‘Mad Max: Fury Road’ Sequel a Title|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/george-miller-mad-max-fury-road-sequel/|website=[[疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路/Film|疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路//Film]]|accessdate=2015-05-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519013857/http://www.slashfilm.com/george-miller-mad-max-fury-road-sequel/|archivedate=2015-05-19|date=2015-05-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=George Miller Promises ‘More Max,’ Starting With ‘Mad Max: The Wasteland’|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/mad-max-george-miller-announces-more-movies-mad-max-the-wasteland-1201499904/|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=[[Penske_Media_Corporation|Penske Media Corporation]]|accessdate=2015-05-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150519013352/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/mad-max-george-miller-announces-more-movies-mad-max-the-wasteland-1201499904/|archivedate=2015-05-19|date=2015-05-18}}</ref>。米勒曾一度傳出他不再執導續集，但於2016年1月的採訪中澄清，之前的話受記者誤解，自己仍會執導續集但不會馬上進行<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://collider.com/george-miller-new-mad-max-movies/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archive-date=2016-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160117100744/http://collider.com/george-miller-new-mad-max-movies/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

